Class CalcCarportMaterials

  • java.lang.Object
    • Util.CalcCarportMaterials

  • public class CalcCarportMaterials
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to calculate materials needed in a carport-skeleton. Has one class variabels carportParts this is used for calculations throughout.
